Keep the Data in the Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking App Up-to-Date

To keep the data in your analytics app current, schedule the app to refresh regularly. This runs the 4 recipes for this app in the correct order. Schedule the app refresh every day outside of normal business hours.

Available in: Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions where B2B Communications Cloud is enabled.
